									<h2>Selected Design: The Balanced Redesign</h2>
									<p>After careful consideration of community needs, budget constraints, and long-term sustainability, the <strong>Balanced Redesign</strong> option has been selected as the final proposal. This approach offers the optimal combination of immediate impact, cost-effectiveness, and future flexibility.</p>
									
									<hr class="major" />
									
									<h2>AI-Generated Redesign Visualization</h2>
									<p>The following images were generated using DALL-E AI, based on Google Maps street view references of Montefiore Square. The AI prompts were carefully crafted to transform existing site conditions into the proposed redesign vision.</p>
									
									<div class="row">
										<div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
											<h3>Current Condition (Reference)</h3>
											<span class="image fit"><img src="images/plaza/current-1.jpg" alt="Current Plaza Condition" /></span>
											<p><em>Source: Google Maps street view of Montefiore Square showing existing hardscape and minimal amenities.</em></p>
										</div>
										<div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
											<h3>Proposed Redesign (AI-Generated)</h3>
											<span class="image fit"><img src="images/plaza/redesign-1.jpg" alt="AI-Generated Redesign" /></span>
											<p><em>AI Prompt: "Transform this Harlem plaza into a vibrant community space with native shade trees, integrated seating walls, permeable paving, solar-powered lighting, and flexible event space. Include diverse community members using the space. Photorealistic architectural rendering, golden hour lighting."</em></p>
										</div>
									</div>
									
									<div class="row">
										<div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
											<h3>Current View from Amsterdam Ave</h3>
											<span class="image fit"><img src="images/plaza/current-2.jpg" alt="Current Amsterdam Avenue View" /></span>
											<p><em>Source: Google Maps showing exposed conditions along Amsterdam Avenue.</em></p>
										</div>
										<div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
											<h3>Proposed Avenue Edge (AI-Generated)</h3>
											<span class="image fit"><img src="images/plaza/redesign-2.jpg" alt="AI-Generated Avenue Redesign" /></span>
											<p><em>AI Prompt: "Redesign this Harlem plaza edge along Amsterdam Avenue with bioswales for stormwater management, tree-lined pedestrian buffer, outdoor seating for nearby cafes, improved lighting, and clear pedestrian crossings. Maintain urban context with historic buildings. Photorealistic rendering."</em></p>
										</div>
									</div>
									
