									<h2>Design Elements</h2>
									
									<div class="row">
										<div class="col-4 col-12-medium">
											<h3>Green Infrastructure</h3>
											<ul>
												<li>12 new native shade trees</li>
												<li>Rain gardens and bioswales</li>
												<li>Permeable paving surfaces</li>
												<li>Drought-tolerant plantings</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
										<div class="col-4 col-12-medium">
											<h3>Comfort & Safety</h3>
											<ul>
												<li>Integrated seating walls</li>
												<li>Modular movable furniture</li>
												<li>LED lighting with smart controls</li>
												<li>Emergency call boxes</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
										<div class="col-4 col-12-medium">
											<h3>Community Features</h3>
											<ul>
												<li>Flexible event space (2,000 sq ft)</li>
												<li>Outdoor exercise equipment</li>
												<li>Community notice boards</li>
												<li>Public art installation areas</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
									</div>
									
									<hr class="major" />
									
									<h2>Implementation Strategy</h2>
									
									<h3>Phase 1: Quick Wins (Months 1-6)</h3>
									<ul>
										<li>Install temporary shade structures</li>
										<li>Add movable seating and tables</li>
										<li>Improve lighting in dark zones</li>
										<li>Paint pedestrian crossings</li>
									</ul>
									
									<h3>Phase 2: Core Improvements (Months 6-18)</h3>
									<ul>
										<li>Tree planting and establishment</li>
										<li>Installation of permanent seating walls</li>
										<li>Paving improvements</li>
										<li>Stormwater infrastructure</li>
									</ul>
									
									<h3>Phase 3: Programming Activation (Ongoing)</h3>
									<ul>
										<li>Community events and markets</li>
										<li>Partnerships with local businesses</li>
										<li>Seasonal programming</li>
										<li>Maintenance and monitoring</li>
									</ul>
									
